    "en": {
      "title": "Train tickets at old price tomorrow too",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Kasun Chamara, Grants Secretary of the Railway Station Master's Association, said today (22) afternoon that tickets can be purchased at the same price as on tomorrow (23) and there is no change in the action against the revision of the ticket fee.",
        "Railway General Manager Dhammika Jayasundara has announced that train fares will be increased by 60 percent from midnight today (22)."
      ],
